headline: Lamb Weston to Announce Fiscal Year 2026 First Quarter Financial Results on September 30, 2025
summary: EAGLE, Idaho, September 02, 2025--Lamb Weston Holdings, Inc. (NYSE: LW) announced today it will report fiscal 2026 first quarter financial results on September 30, 2025. The news release will be issued at approximately 8:30 a.m. ET, followed by a conference call at 10:00 a.m. ET.
